<item>
            <title>[SPARK-19882] Pivot with null as the pivot value throws NPE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-19882</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This seems a regression.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Spark 1.6&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Seq(Tuple1(None), Tuple1(Some(1))).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).groupBy($&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).pivot(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).count().show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;prints&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;+----+----+---+
|   a|&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;|  1|
+----+----+---+
|&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;|   0|  0|
|   1|   0|  1|
+----+----+---+
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Current master&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;Seq(Tuple1(None), Tuple1(Some(1))).toDF(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).groupBy($&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).pivot(&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&quot;a&quot;&lt;/span&gt;).count().show()
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;prints&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;java.lang.NullPointerException was thrown.
java.lang.NullPointerException
  at org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.expressions.aggregate.PivotFirst$$anonfun$4.apply(PivotFirst.scala:145)
  at org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.expressions.aggregate.PivotFirst$$anonfun$4.apply(PivotFirst.scala:143)
  at scala.collection.immutable.List.map(List.scala:273)
  at org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.expressions.aggregate.PivotFirst.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(PivotFirst.scala:143)
  at org.apache.spark.sql.catalyst.analysis.Analyzer$ResolvePivot$$anonfun$apply$7$$anonfun$24.apply(Analyzer.scala:509)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
